    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/496fdd81024c28bf65e98f5638a85a2b.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/496fdd81024c28bf65e98f5638a85a2b.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=26 height=22 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【故事简介】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个“肉体分裂症”（俗称「幽灵化」）蔓延的社会中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人们早已习惯了幽灵化现象的存在，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清扫员清理幽灵，也成了理所当然的日常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/529054f7c36450563155608795e74351.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/529054f7c36450563155608795e74351.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角里卡尔多靠打零工当幽灵清扫员，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猎杀城市中横行的幽灵肉，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >靠这一行挣些辛苦钱维生……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/faa36daad06586c397e70299943bcc6e.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/faa36daad06586c397e70299943bcc6e.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=22 height=41 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【游戏简介】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是一款使用 RPG Maker VX Ace 制作的 RPG 游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的世界观：描绘了幽灵化成为日常的黑暗又荒诞的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜要素：通过解开谜团和拼图，深入幽灵的精神世界，推进剧情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注重剧情：在探索过程中揭示幽灵的内心与过往</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怀旧风格：像素画面与BGM营造出经典RPG Maker的复古氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特系统：用香烟存档、用“睡觉”恢复体力等别出心裁的系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/4756946f4f2fcefe356d692b0f868939.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/4756946f4f2fcefe356d692b0f868939.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=30 height=49 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【操作方式】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z键 ：确认</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X键 ：打开菜单 / 取消</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方向键 ：移动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift键 ：奔跑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >存档方式 ：使用香烟或烟蒂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >行动→睡觉：体力不足时可进行恢复</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F5键 ：切换全屏 / 窗口模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F12键 ：强制返回标题（不保存）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/5be6fb654ed6dbbfdb70535755258301.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/5be6fb654ed6dbbfdb70535755258301.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=30 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【推荐给这些玩家】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怀旧游戏爱好者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢解谜游戏的玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢剧情驱动型游戏的玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢黑色幽默与复古风RPG的朋友</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/736a97f78cc9756d74cd8ead8fbfd927.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/736a97f78cc9756d74cd8ead8fbfd927.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=34 height=58 /></picture></span></p>",
